data.description: Come home to this amazing MULTI GENERATIONAL LIVING move in ready home with an additional living unit.  This wonderful family home is nestled on a rear end cul-de-sac among this newer beautiful neighborhood of Romoland / Menifee. On those cool nights enjoy a stroll on the lovely streets winding throughout the family friendly neighborhood.  When it's time to unwind in your amazingly bright and open new home, flip on the whole house fan, open a window and you'll feel right at home relaxing in the huge oversized open living room. Enjoy the outdoors and fresh air on your large patio area and huge back yard perfect for pets or kids or adding a pool, BBQ or jacuzzi.  You'll always have something to do when your new home is so close to so many amazing attractions like parks, trails, a waterpark, Big League Dreams Baseball park and much more.  Conveniently located near the 215 fwy to get where you're going.  This home is perfect first-time home buyers, new families and especially the multigenerational family with the additional upstairs living area with it's own kitchen, bathroom and sperate and attached entrances.  Your family will love being so close just upstairs, yet with their own privacy.  Or even rent out the upstairs unit for additional income.  Plus, ton's of parking for the large family or guests!  This great neighborhood in this area one won't last!  Get it before it's gone!
